\f0\fs24 \cf0 In order to properly delve into the research on the psychedelic class of drugs, it must first be clearly defined. Terrence McKenna was one of the most eminent researchers in this field. His research, presented in the book Food of the Gods outlines the history of these drugs, and their meaning in culture. McKenna outlines psychedelic drugs as follows:\
