\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}At present day, drugs are almost entirely used for recreational or medicinal purposes.\
{\listtext	2.	}Psychedelic drugs enable easy communication with a universal {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://63DE4854-DD53-4AC8-AD53-D4D9747F4CE9"}}{\fldrslt consciousness}} through reliable production of altered states of consciousness.\
{\listtext	3.	}Despite the intentional oppression of the use of psychedelic drugs, it is people, i.e. groups that kept their use alive. The role of these people is archetypically significant, and observable across cultures and eras.\
\pard\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
